      "when_to_use": "When you need missing value imputation and risk table mapping but NOT feature selection. Used when feature set is already curated but data quality requires preprocessing. Similar to training_with_feature_selection but without the feature pruning step.",
      "when_not_to_use": "If you also need feature selection (use training_with_feature_selection). If data is already clean (use training_with_evaluation). If you need registration (use complete_e2e).",
